description.en: Chizuru is the new school nurse and she's eager not just to heal physical injuries but also injuries of the heart. She soon meets Kuga, a student whose father is a powerful yet sleazy politician who Kuga hates with a passion. At first Kuga just tries to avoid Chizuru's attempts to help him, but as time goes on he finds himself attracted to her. Yet Chizuru has her own demons that get in the way of her being able to fall in love again. What will happen between the two? The story progresses through Chizuru's repeated attempts to help all sorts of students, most of whom don't want to be helped!
